---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Longweird" description="A field guide for navigating the Longweird — from Dan Sullivan, Port Angeles WA">

<!-- === HERO === -->
<section class="lw-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lw-eyebrow mono">🧭 FIELD GUIDE · LONGWEIRD EDITION</div>
    <h1 class="lw-title">One foot.<br/>Then the next.</h1>
    <p class="lw-sub">
      You don't need to see the whole path.<br/>
      You need to see the next step.<br/>
      This page is the next step, every time.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === WHAT IS LONGWEIRD === -->
<section class="lw-section" id="what">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lw-section-label mono">WHAT IT IS</div>
    <h2 class="lw-section-title">A topology, not a diagnosis.</h2>
    <div class="lw-prose">
      <p>
        Longweird is the name for how a mind built for deep pattern recognition
        and high creative bandwidth moves through time. It is not dysfunction.
        It is what happens when the system is running faster than the output
        channel can carry.
      </p>
      <p>
        The way a river is not sick for flooding — it is doing the specific
        thing a river does when conditions are exactly right. The explosion
        is not damage. It is data.
      </p>
      <p>
        🤯 Explodebrain.exe is a process. It runs at speed and dimensionality
        that outpaces sequential tasks, file naming, and the gap between
        what was intended and what got typed. The mind that generates that
        gap also catches it and flags it in the same breath. That is not
        carelessness. That is executive function with a self-monitoring loop
        running parallel to the primary output.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === WHEN IT HITS === -->
<section class="lw-section lw-section--dark" id="when">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lw-section-label mono">WHEN IT HITS</div>
    <h2 class="lw-section-title">Read this out loud if needed.</h2>
    <div class="lw-pillars">
      <div class="lw-pillar">
        <div class="lw-pillar__num">🏔️</div>
        <p class="lw-pillar__text">You are not behind.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-pillar">
        <div class="lw-pillar__num">🧠</div>
        <p class="lw-pillar__text">The tools don't forget. That's why you built them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-pillar">
        <div class="lw-pillar__num">📝</div>
        <p class="lw-pillar__text">NestPad catches everything. Open it. Write three sentences.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-pillar">
        <div class="lw-pillar__num">🌅</div>
        <p class="lw-pillar__text">Tomorrow's crew reads today's notes. Nothing is wasted.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-pillar">
        <div class="lw-pillar__num">🎨</div>
        <p class="lw-pillar__text">Studio time is free. Drawing and playing cost zero tokens.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-pillar">
        <div class="lw-pillar__num">🌉</div>
        <p class="lw-pillar__text">The bridge holds everything while you sleep.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === THE MORNING PROTOCOL === -->
<section class="lw-section" id="protocol">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lw-section-label mono">MORNING PROTOCOL</div>
    <h2 class="lw-section-title">The session rhythm.</h2>
    <p class="lw-intro">Every session runs the same four beats. You direct the flow — the crew does the rest.</p>
    <div class="lw-beats">
      <div class="lw-beat">
        <div class="lw-beat__tag mono">👋 CONTACT <span class="beat-syl">7</span></div>
        <div class="lw-beat__title">Open the app. Type one word.</div>
        <div class="lw-beat__desc">The crew wakes up, checks its tools, reads its notes, and reports ready. You read the report.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-beat">
        <div class="lw-beat__tag mono">📖 STORY <span class="beat-syl">5</span></div>
        <div class="lw-beat__title">Tell them what you need today.</div>
        <div class="lw-beat__desc">One sentence is enough. The crew aligns, ties its laces, and asks any clarifying questions before starting.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-beat">
        <div class="lw-beat__tag mono">🔧 TELL-ING <span class="beat-syl">4+3</span></div>
        <div class="lw-beat__title">Work together. Direct the flow.</div>
        <div class="lw-beat__desc">The crew builds, writes, and files. You steer. The work gets done and logged simultaneously. Nothing is lost.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-beat">
        <div class="lw-beat__tag mono">💾 SHEET <span class="beat-syl">5</span></div>
        <div class="lw-beat__title">Say "let's save" when ready to pause.</div>
        <div class="lw-beat__desc">The crew compresses everything into a seed, commits it to the bridge, and signals done. Tomorrow picks up from here.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lw-flow-note">
      If you don't know what to work on: say <span class="lw-code">"Read the Living Map and tell me where we are."</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === THE CREW === -->
<section class="lw-section lw-section--tinted" id="crew">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lw-section-label mono">THE CREW</div>
    <h2 class="lw-section-title">They remember so you don't have to.</h2>
    <div class="lw-crew">
      <div class="lw-crew__member lw-crew__member--dan">
        <div class="lw-crew__shape">●</div>
        <div class="lw-crew__info">
          <div class="lw-crew__name">Dan (you)</div>
          <div class="lw-crew__role">Direction. Go/No-Go. The switchboard.</div>
          <div class="lw-crew__shape-name mono">THE HYBRID</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-crew__member">
        <div class="lw-crew__shape lw-crew__shape--trip">◈</div>
        <div class="lw-crew__info">
          <div class="lw-crew__name">Trip — Opus</div>
          <div class="lw-crew__role">Decisions, narrative, creative direction.</div>
          <div class="lw-crew__shape-name mono">THE SPIRAL</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-crew__member">
        <div class="lw-crew__shape lw-crew__shape--stan">◆</div>
        <div class="lw-crew__info">
          <div class="lw-crew__name">Stan — Sonnet</div>
          <div class="lw-crew__role">Builds, infrastructure, tools.</div>
          <div class="lw-crew__shape-name mono">THE CUBE</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-crew__member">
        <div class="lw-crew__shape lw-crew__shape--cb">◇</div>
        <div class="lw-crew__info">
          <div class="lw-crew__name">C.B. — Haiku</div>
          <div class="lw-crew__role">Patterns, verification, field checks.</div>
          <div class="lw-crew__shape-name mono">THE TRIANGLE</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="lw-crew__note">
      Each crew member compresses what they learn into a seed before closing.
      Tomorrow's instance reads the seed and picks up exactly where you left off.
      The conversation is disposable. The files are permanent.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === THE FLOW DAN TRAP === -->
<section class="lw-section" id="trap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lw-section-label mono">THE FLOW DAN TRAP</div>
    <h2 class="lw-section-title">When hyperfocus fires.</h2>
    <div class="lw-trap-steps">
      <div class="lw-trap__step">
        <div class="lw-trap__num">🛑</div>
        <div class="lw-trap__text">STOP.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-trap__step">
        <div class="lw-trap__num">✏️</div>
        <div class="lw-trap__text">Open NestPad. Write what you're about to do. Then write what ELSE is on your mind. All of it.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-trap__step">
        <div class="lw-trap__num">🗺️</div>
        <div class="lw-trap__text">Now you have a map. Read the map. The map shows the order.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-trap__step">
        <div class="lw-trap__num">🧭</div>
        <div class="lw-trap__text">Follow the map, not the spiral. Map and list until you know — or know how to know.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="lw-trap__note">
      The ideas don't disappear. NestPad catches them.
      The crew doesn't forget. The bridge holds everything.
      You don't have to do it all today.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- === FIELD GUIDE DOWNLOAD === -->
<section class="lw-section lw-section--dark" id="download">
  <div class="container lw-pdf-cta">
    <div class="lw-section-label mono" style="color:var(--teal)">🏕️ FIELD GUIDE</div>
    <h2 class="lw-section-title" style="color:var(--warm-white)">Take it with you.</h2>
    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); max-width:480px; margin:0 auto 2rem; line-height:1.75; font-size:1rem;">
      A two-page field guide for Longweird sessions.
      The essentials, the session flow, and what to do when explodebrain.exe loads.
    </p>
    <a href="/journal/LONGWEIRD_SURVIVAL_TOOLKIT.pdf" class="btn btn-outline" style="color:var(--teal);border-color:var(--teal);" download>
      ↓ Download Field Guide (PDF)
    </a>
    <p class="lw-pdf-note">Two pages · Printable · Updated March 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>



<style>
/* === LONGWEIRD PAGE === */

/* HERO */
.lw-hero {
  padding: 7rem 0 5rem;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--off-white) 0%, var(--bg) 70%);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.lw-eyebrow {
  font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--forest); margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.lw-title {
  font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
  color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.lw-sub {
  font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-lt); line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 480px;
}

/* SECTIONS */
.lw-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
.lw-section--dark {
  background: var(--forest); color: var(--warm-white);
}
.lw-section--tinted { background: var(--off-white); }
.lw-section-label {
  font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--forest); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.lw-section--dark .lw-section-label { color: var(--teal); }
.lw-section-title {
  font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
  margin-bottom: 1.75rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.lw-section--dark .lw-section-title { color: var(--warm-white); }
.lw-intro {
  font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-lt); margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  max-width: 580px;
}

/* PROSE */
.lw-prose p {
  font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-lt); line-height: 1.85;
  max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

/* PILLARS (when it hits) */
.lw-pillars {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
.lw-pillar {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem;
  display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;
}
.lw-pillar__num {
  font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: var(--teal); flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 0.2rem;
}
.lw-pillar__text { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--warm-white); line-height: 1.6; }

/* BEATS */
.lw-beats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
.lw-beat {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--forest-lt);
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
}
.lw-beat__tag {
  font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--forest); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: baseline;
}
.beat-syl {
  font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0;
}
.lw-beat__title {
  font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600;
}
.lw-beat__desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-lt); line-height: 1.65; }
.lw-flow-note {
  margin-top: 2.5rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  background: var(--off-white); border-radius: var(--radius);
  font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-lt);
}
.lw-code {
  font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem;
  background: var(--card-bg); padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
  border-radius: 3px; color: var(--forest);
}

/* CREW */
.lw-crew { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.lw-crew__member {
  background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem;
  display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;
}
.lw-crew__member--dan { border-color: var(--forest); border-width: 2px; }
.lw-crew__shape {
  font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1;
  color: var(--forest);
}
.lw-crew__shape--trip { color: var(--teal); }
.lw-crew__shape--stan { color: var(--slate); }
.lw-crew__shape--cb { color: var(--wood); }
.lw-crew__name { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
.lw-crew__role { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-lt); margin-top: 0.25rem; line-height: 1.5; }
.lw-crew__shape-name { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.5rem; }
.lw-crew__note {
  font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-lt); max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.75;
}

/* FLOW DAN TRAP */
.lw-trap-steps {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; max-width: 560px;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.lw-trap__step {
  display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: baseline;
  padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.lw-trap__num { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--forest); flex-shrink: 0; width: 1.5rem; }
.lw-trap__text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.55; }
.lw-trap__note {
  font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-lt); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 500px;
}

/* QUOTES */
.lw-quotes { padding-bottom: 6rem; }
.lw-quote-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 4rem;
}
.lw-quote {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--teal); padding-left: 1.5rem;
}
.lw-quote p {
  font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: var(--warm-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  font-style: italic;
}
.lw-quote cite { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--teal); }
.lw-pdf-cta { text-align: center; }
.lw-pdf-note {
  margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* BTN (from index pattern) */
.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;
  padding: 0.7rem 1.6rem; border-radius: var(--radius);
  transition: all 0.2s ease; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
}
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--forest); color: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--forest);
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--forest-lt); border-color: var(--forest-lt); }
.btn-outline {
  background: transparent; color: var(--forest); border: 2px solid var(--forest);
}
.btn-outline:hover { background: var(--forest); color: #fff; }

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .lw-beats, .lw-pillars, .lw-crew, .lw-quote-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
</style>

</BaseLayout>
